tc_game_config_files.template: sv_servername="$[HostName]" //The server name that's displayed in the server browser window - this overrides the server name specified in the command line steam_ugc=![steamugc] http_password=$[RConPassword] //The password used to connect via rcon g_pinglimit=![pinglimit] //Max ping a player can have before being kicked (0=disabled), default: 1000 g_pingLimitTimer=![pingLimitTimer] //Time in seconds after which a player will be kicked if they are over the specified ping limit, default: 15 g_gameRules_Camera=![gameRulesCamera] //Server enforced camera rules, 0=both, 1=first person only, 2=third person only in vehicle wm_disable=![wmdisable] //Completely disable the weather management system wm_timeScale=![wmtimeScale] //Scale time of day speed, default: 1 wm_timeScaleWeather=![wmtimeScaleWeather] //Scale of weather speed, default: 1 wm_timeScaleNight=![wmtimeScaleNight] //Scale of night speed (relative to day), default: 4 wm_timeOffset=![wmtimeOffset] //Time offset to system time, negative = random offset, use 24-x for real negative offsets (as positive numbers), default: 0 wm_forceTime=-![wmforceTime] //Force the server time to a specific 24-hour time, default: -1 (disabled), can be from 0.0 through 24.0 sv_noBannedAccounts=![svnoBannedAccounts] //Don't allow any banned steam accounts to join (or those with a private profile), default: 0 sv_maxuptime=![svmaxuptime] //Maximum server uptime until restart in hours, default: 24 (whitelisted), 12 otherwise - cannot exceed 24 hours schedule_shutdown_utc=![scheduleshutdownutc] //Hard shutdown of the game at the specified UTC hour, can have multiples of these in the hosting.cfg file if wanted sv_motd="![svmotd]" //Server motd to display when players join the server sv_url="![svurl]" //Server url to display when players join the server - just a second motd line really sv_msg_conn=![svmsgconn] //Announce connections in chat (whitelisted feature only), default: 0 sv_msg_death=![svmsgdeath] //Announce deaths in chat (whitelisted feature only), default: 0 g_gameRules_bases=![gameRulesbases] //Server enforced base placement rules, default: 1 (0=no bases, 1=restricted zones, 2=bases everywhere(whitelisted feature only)) g_playerHealthRegen=![gplayerHealthRegen] //Health regeneration speed, default: 0.111 g_playerFoodDecay=![gplayerFoodDecay] //Food decay speed, default: 0.2777 g_playerFoodDecaySprinting=![gplayerFoodDecaySprinting] //Food decay speed when sprinting, default: 0.34722 g_playerWaterDecay=![gplayerWaterDecay] //Water decay speed, default: 0.4861 g_playerWaterDecaySprinting=![gplayerWaterDecaySprinting] //Water decay speed when sprinting, default: 0.607638 g_playerInfiniteStamina=![gplayerInfiniteStamina] //Enable infinite stamina, default: 0 g_craftingSpeedMultiplier=![gcraftingSpeedMultiplier] //Scalar to accelerate crafting times, default: 1 asm_disable=![asmdisable] //Disable the AI spawner manager system, default: 0 asm_percent=![asmpercent] //Set the AI spawner location percentage, default: 33 (max is 90) - this helps control the AI spawn density asm_maxMultiplier=![asmmaxMultiplier] //Set the multiplier for the AI spawner max amount, default: 1 (max 5) asm_hordeCooldown=![asmhordeCooldown] //Set the min cooldown on spawning hordes, default (in seconds): 900 pcs_maxCorpses=![pcsmaxCorpses] //Set the maximum number of player corpses, default: 20 pcs_maxCorpseTime=![pcsmaxCorpseTime] //Set the maximum time before a player corpse will despawn, default (in seconds): 1200 steam_inventory_enable=![steaminventoryenable] //Configure the Steam inventory (kiosk system), default: 0 (0=fully enabled, 3=admin disabled, do not use 1 or 2)
